OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FThe fines cover a catalogue of errors
OL,7,Fcarried out by water companies in
OL,8,Frecent years, as ITV News' reporter
OL,9,FSangeeta Kandola and Business Editor
OL,10,FJoel Hills reports
OL,12,FOfwat has proposed #168 million worth
OL,13,Fof fines for three of England's
OL,14,Fbiggest water companies for failing to
OL,15,Flimit river pollution, including a
OL,16,F#104 million fine for crisis-hit
OL,17,FThames Water.
