OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FOfwat said it had "uncovered a
OL,7,Fcatalogue of failure" by three of
OL,8,FEngland's biggest water firms
OL,9,Fresulting in "excessive spills from
OL,10,Fstorm overflows".
OL,12,FOfwat's chief executive David Black
OL,13,Fsaid: "Our investigation has shown how
OL,14,Fthey routinely released sewage into
OL,15,Four rivers and seas, rather than
OL,16,Fensuring that this only happens in
OL,17,Fexceptional circumstances as the law
OL,18,Fintends."
