OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FThe other two companies being fined
OL,7,Fare Yorkshire Water for #47 million
OL,8,Fand Northumbrian Water for #17 million.
OL,10,FThe fines are part of the water
OL,11,Fregulator's come from the first batch
OL,12,Fof results from its biggest ever
OL,13,Finvestigation into the industry.
OL,15,FThe penalties relate to water firms'
OL,16,Fmanagement of their wastewater
OL,17,Ftreatment and sewer systems, which
OL,18,Fhave come under heavy criticism for
OL,19,Freleasing too much pollution into
OL,20,Frivers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
