OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FThe fines are currently only a
OL,7,Fproposal with the companies having
OL,8,Funtil early September to appeal them
OL,9,Fbefore Ofwat makes a final decision on
OL,10,Fwhether to impose them.
OL,12,FIn an announcement on Tuesday morning,
OL,13,FOfwat said the firms "failed to ensure
OL,14,Fthat discharges of untreated
OL,15,Fwastewater from storm overflows occur
OL,16,Fonly in exceptional circumstances,
OL,17,Fwhich has resulted in harm to the
OL,18,Fenvironment and their customers."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
