OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FIt added that there was a "strong
OL,7,Fcorrelation" between high spill levels
OL,8,Fand operational issues at their
OL,9,Fwastewater treatment sites, "which
OL,10,Fpoints to these companies not having
OL,11,Fproperly operated and maintained their
OL,12,Fwastewater treatment works."
OL,14,FIt said the firms had failed to
OL,15,Fupgrade their assets where necessary,
OL,16,Fand had been slow to grasp their
OL,17,Fobligations to limit pollution from
OL,18,Fstorm overflows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
