OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FOfwat said that more than two-thirds
OL,7,Fof Thames Water's wastewater treatment
OL,8,Fworks with Flow to Full Treatment
OL,9,F(FFT) permits had capacity and
OL,10,Foperational issues, while one-in-six
OL,11,Fof its storm overflows were found to
OL,12,Fbe in breach of regulations.
OL,14,FYorkshire Water's wastewater treatment
OL,15,Fworks were in better shape, with just
OL,16,F16% of them having operational issues.
OL,17,FBut 45% of its storm overflows were in
OL,18,Fbreach.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
