OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,FAnd 3% of Northumbrian Water's
OL,7,Fwastewater works had issues, while 9%
OL,8,Fof its storm overflows were in breach.
OL,10,FBlack said the stress of the fines
OL,11,Fwould fall on the three water firms
OL,12,Finvestors not the customers.
OL,14,FSpeaking to Sky News he said: "We set
OL,15,Fthe rules on what charges they can
OL,16,Frecover from customers, so we make
OL,17,Fabsolutely no provision for fines in
OL,18,Fthe levels of bills that is set for
OL,19,Fcustomers."
