OL,11,FHe also acknowledged the perilous
OL,12,Fstate of Thames Water which is
OL,13,Fstruggling with billions of debt but
OL,14,Fsaid it was not a "not a relevant
OL,15,Fconsideration" when considering
OL,16,Fimposing fines.
OL,18,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed
OL,19,Fwelcomed the fines.
