OL,3,CWater companies face biggest ever
OL,4,Cfines over sewage spills
OL,6,F"The unacceptable destruction of our
OL,7,Fwaterways should never have been
OL,8,Fallowed ` and it is right that those
OL,9,Fresponsible for illegally polluting
OL,10,Four rivers, lakes and seas face the
OL,11,Fconsequences," he said.
OL,13,FCharles Watson, chairman of the
OL,14,Fcampaign group River Action, said:
OL,15,F"Thankfully the water regulator, for
OL,16,Fso long toothless, is finally waking
OL,17,Fup to the scale of the public's
OL,18,Foutrage and we are starting to see
OL,19,Fsome meaningful penalties being
OL,20,Fimposed upon the worst offenders."
